{"type": "article", "id": 15470, "title": "Vans秋冬防水系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-24T06:34:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 81, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122442DKQ723p9oACqNek4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tVans 推出今年秋冬系列 Mountain Edition，采用防水材质，并在内部采用保暖措施以适应季节变化。其中 Sk8-Hi MTE 和 Old Skool MTE 两款鞋采用 Scotchgard™ 防水技术，搭配麂皮等皮革材质，在鞋内加上绒面羊毛鞋垫。而夹棉衬衣和夹克等单品大多采用防水涂层和 PrimaLoft 保暖衬，轻便保暖。<a href=\"http://www.vans.com/shop/mte-designed-for-the-elements#beginIndex=0&amp;facet%5B%5D=ads_f14001_ntk_cs%25253A%252522Footwear%252522\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261425561ht2nVflmcAYR4gT.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142557B5O6l0pnWjQrthAP.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142558hc2qEkmePj1XAIFn.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142558uLvEsJ52GCafVZXH.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}